<ul>

<li>
<p>
<a href="http://perlhacks.com/2012/03/you-must-hate-version-control-systems/">“You
Must Hate Version Control Systems”</a> - a post on the “Perl Hacks” blog about
best practices in the software industry.
</p>
</li>
